sign.text: i can use my energy radar arrow to find the large forest spirits. Once I have collected all of them I will have drained this horribly pleasent planet, leaving a stinky dead dust ball. just how i like them.
A lovely big forest spirit to fuel my mining machines. I must collect all of these. Should my mighty but delicate body get destroyed i will be reborn at the last mining machine i walked past!
if i press the up arrow he flaps his wings. I shall enjoy flying this slave! When i tire of these creatures i press the monster exit button (x key) to make them explode! i like that bit the best!
The first energy mining machine is ready! Time to explore this twee world using the arrow keys.
a sweet happy kitty?...he is bigger than i expected, i must be careful not to touch these giant creatures but If i jump on to just his head i can control him. i shall make him a tool of evil!
